ComfyUI-Mega-ASR

This project includes a ComfyUI wrapper and built-in inference adapter for Mega-ASR.
Portions of the inference adapter are adapted from the official Mega-ASR project:
https://github.com/xzf-thu/Mega-ASR.git

Mega-ASR model weights are distributed by their original authors at:
https://huggingface.co/zhifeixie/Mega-ASR
